name: Solidex Volatile Yield Seeker
description: Supplies {{token}} to a [Solidex Finance](https://solidexfinance.com/#/pools) Volatile Pool to earn SOLID and SEX. Earned tokens are harvested, sold for more {{token}} which is deposited back into the strategy.
